    "data": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی وَلِیِّ اللّٰہِ وَ حَبِیْبِہٖ\nPeace be on the favorite of Allah,\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی خَلِیْلِ اللّٰہِ وَ نَجِیْبِہٖ \nPeace be on the beloved friend of Allah, His distinguished hero!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی صَفِیِّ اللّٰہِ وَ ابْنِ صَفِیِّہٖ \nPeace be on the choicest confidant of Allah, sincerely attached precisely like his father!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْحُسَیْنِ الْمَظْلُوْمِ الشَّھِیْدِ \nPeace be on Husain, who gave his life in the way of Allah, a martyr, underwent untold hardships\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَسِیْرِ الْکُرُبَاتِ وَ قَتِیْلِ الْعَبَرَاتِ \nPeace be on the hostage surrounded by the-tightening circle of sorrow and grief, killed by a horde of savages.\nاَللّٰھُمَّ اِنِّیْٓ اَشْھَدُ اَنَّہٗ وَلِیُّکَ وَ ابْنُ وَلِیِّکَ \nO my Allah! I give witness that beyond a shadow of doubt he is Your favorite and choicest confidant, who enjoys Your confidence and favor, precisely like his father!\nوَ صَفِیُّکَ وَ ابْنُ صَفِیِّکَ الْفَآئِزُ بِکَرَامَتِکَ \nYou looked upto him and elected him in Your cause,\nاَکْرَمْتَہٗ بِالشَّھَادَۃِ وَ حَبَوْتَہٗ بِالسَّعَادَۃِ \npicked and chose him for the good fortune, selected for him the best purified parents,\nوَ اجْتَبَیْتَہٗ بِطِیْبِ الْوِلَادَۃِ وَجَعَلْتَہٗ سَیِّدًا مِّنَ السَّادَۃِ \nappointed him guardian, leader, and defender of rights.\nوَ قَآئِدًا مِّنَ الْقَادَۃِ وَ ذَائِدًا مِّنَ الذَّادَۃِ \na true representative (inheritor and progenitor) of guardians, leaders and defenders of rights. \nوَ اَعْطَیْتَہٗ مَوَارِیْثَ الْاَنْبِیْآءِ وَ جَعَلْتَہٗ حُجَّۃً عَلٰی خَلْقِکَ مِنَ الْاَوْصِیَآءِ \ngave him much and more from the inheritance of the Prophets, put him forward as a decisive argument, along with the other successors (of the Holy Prophet-the twelve Imams) to the mankind.\nفَاعْذَرَ فِیْ الدُّعَآءِ وَ مَنَحَ النُّصْحَ وَ بَذَلَ مُھْجَتَہٗ فِیْکَ \nHe met with deadly dangers, acted justly and fairly, made use of everything belonging to him to pay full attention to give sincere advice, took pains, made every effort and put his heart, mind, soul and life at the disposal of Your mission\nلِیَسْتَنْقِذَ عِبَادَکَ مِنَ الْجَھَالَۃِ وَ حَیْرَۃِ الضَّلَا لَۃِ \nto liberate the people from the yoke of ignorance and evil of bewilderment, but an evildoer,\nوَ قَدْ تَوَازَرَ عَلَیْہِ مَنْ غَرَّتْہُ الدُّنْیَا \ndeceived with empty hopes of mean and worthless worldly gains, \nوَ بَاعَ حَظَّہٗ بِالْاَرْذَلِ الْاَدْنٰی \nhad pressed heavily on him, and sold out his share (eternal bliss)\nوَ شَرٰی اٰخِرَتَہٗ بِالثَّمَنِ الْاَوْکَسِ وَ تَغْطَرَسَ \nfor the meanest and lowest bargain, betrayed his “day of judgment” for a vulgar return,.\nوَ تَرَدّٰی فِیْ ھَوَاہُ وَ اَسْخَطَکَ وَ اَسْخَطَ نَبِیِّکَ \ntook pride In insolence, fell into the fathom-well of silly stupid follies, provoked You and Your Prophet to anger,\nوَ اَطَاعَ مِنْ عِبَادِکَ اَھْلَ الشِّقَاقِ وَ النِّفَاقِ \ndid as the harsh discordant, the hypocrite,\nوَ حَمَلَۃَ الْاَوْزَارِ الْمُسْتَوْجِبِیْنَ النَّارَ فَجَاھَدَھُمْ فِیْکَ \nthe heavily burdened bearers of sin, condemned to Hellfire, advised to him, however, he (the Holy Imam),\nصَابِرًا مُّحْتَسِبًا حَتّٰی سُفِکَ فِیْ طَاعَتِکَ دَمُہٗ \nsteadily, rightly and justly coped with them,\nوَ اسْتُبِیْحَ حَرِیْمُہٗ\ntill, in Your obedience, gave his life after which his family was set adrift.\nاَللّٰہُمَّ فَالْعَنْہُمْ لَعْنًا وَبِیْلاً وَّ عَذِّبْہُمْ عَذَابًا اَلِیْمًا \nO my Allah, therefore, condemn them to hell as a denunciation and conviction; and crack-down on them with a painful Punishment.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکَ یَابْنَ رَسُوْلِ اللّٰہِ \nPeace be on you O the son of the Messenger of Allah!\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکَ یَابْنَ سَیِّدِ الْاَوْصِیَآءِ \nPeace be on you 0 the son of the first of the successors (of the Holy Prophet)!\nاَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ اَمِیْنُ اللّٰہِ وَ ابْنَ اَمِیْنِہٖ \nI bear witness that Allah put faith in you like He had full confidence in your father, and that you always looked for and collected good and virtue.\nعِشْتَ سَعِیْدًا وَ مَضَیْتَ حَمِیْدًا \nlived a highly praiseworthy life\nوَ مُتَّ فَقِیْدًا مَظْلُوْمًا شَہِیْدًا \nand departed from this world a martyr, forsaken and abused;\nوَ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّ اللّٰہَ مُنْجِزٌ مَّا وَعَدَکَ وَ مُہْلِکٌ مَّنْ خَذَلَکَ \nI bear witness that Allah will promptly fulfill the promise, He made to you,\nوَ مُعَذِّبٌ مَّنْ قَتَلَکَ وَ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ وَفَیْتَ بِعَہْدِ اللّٰہِ \nand destroy those who left you helpless and punish those who killed you; I bear witness that you kept your promise made with Allah,\nوَ جَاہَدْتَ فِیْ سَبِیْلِہٖ حَتّٰی اَتٰیکَ الْیَقِیْنُ \nand strived in His way till what was certain came upon you,\nفَلَعَنَ اللّٰہُ مَنْ قَتَلَکَ وَ لَعَنَ اللّٰہُ مَنْ ظَلَمَکَ \nso curse of Allah be on those who killed you, curse of Allah be on those who oppressed you,\nوَ لَعَنَ اللّٰہُ اُمَّۃً سَمِعَتْ بِذٰلِکَ فَرَضِیَتْ بِہٖ \ncurse of Allah be on the people who came to know and approved\nاَللّٰہُمَّ اِنِّیْ اُشْہِدُکَ اَنِّیْ وَلِیٌّ لِّمَنْ وَالَاہُ وَ عَدُوٌّ لِّمَنْ عَادَاہُ \nO my Allah be my witness that I make friends with those who love him and oppose those who deny him.\nبِاَبِیْ اَنْتَ وَ اُمِّیْ یَابْنَ رَسُوْلِ اللّٰہِ \nI, my father and mother, are at your disposal O the son of the Messenger of Allah.\nاَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ کُنْتَ نُوْرًا فِیْ الْاَصْلَابِ الشَّامِخَۃِ \nI know and bear witness that you were “light” in the sublime loins\nوَ الْاَرْحَامِ الْمُطَہَّرَۃِ \nand in the pure wombs,\nلَمْ تُنَجِّسْکَ الْجَاہِلِیَّۃُ بِاَنْجَاسِہَا \nnever touched you the dirt of ignorance,\nوَ لَمْ تُلْبِسْکَ الْمُدْلَہِمَّاتُ مِنْ ثِیَابِہَا \nnor ever obscurity concealed you in its folds;\nوَ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ مِنْ دَعَآئِمِ الدِّیْنِ وَ اَرْکَانِ الْمُسْلِمِیْنَ \nI bear witness that you are the pillar of “Deen”, support of the Muslims,\nوَ مَعْقِلِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّکَ الْاِمَامُ الْبَرُّ التَّقِیُّ الرَّضِیُّ الزَّکِیُّ \nrefuge of the faithful; I bear witness that you are a truthful, well-aware, content, intelligent,\nالْہَادِیْ الْمَہْدِیُّ وَ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّ الْاَئِمَّۃَ مِنْ وُلْدِکَ \nrightly guided guide (Imam); I bear witness that the Imams among your descendants\nکَلِمَۃُ التَّقْوٰی وَ اَعْلَامُ الْہُدٰی وَ الْعُرْوَۃُ الْوُثْقٰی \nare the symbols of “conscious piety” and signs of “true guidance”, the “safe handle” – lslam,\nوَ الْحُجَّۃُ عَلٰی اَہْلِ الدُّنْیَا وَ اَشْہَدُ اَنِّیْ بِکُمْ مُؤْمِنٌ \nand the decisive arguments over mankind; I declare positively that I have full faith in you\nوَّ بِاِیَابِکُمْ مُوْقِنٌۢ بِشَرَایِعِ دِیْنِیْ وَ خَوَاتِیْمِ عَمَلِیْ \nand I know for certain that you shall return. I am, fully committed to the laws of my religion, certain of my deeds,\nوَ قَلْبِیْ لِقَلْبِکُمْ سِلْمٌ وَّ اَمْرِیْ لِاَمْرِکُمْ مُتَّبِعٌ \nmy mind and heart ready for your return,\nوَّ نُصْرَتِیْ لَکُمْ مُعَدَّۃٌ \nand my affairs carried out in the light of your instructions,\nحَتّٰی یَاْذَنَ اللّٰہُ لَکُمْ \ntill Allah gives you permission, together with you,\nفَمَعَکُمْ مَعَكُمْ لَا مَعَ عَدُوِّکُمْ صَلَوَاتُ اللّٰہِ عَلَیْکُمْ \nalong with you, not at the same time with your enemies. Blessings of Allah be on you,\nوَ عَلٰی اَرْوَاحِکُمْ وَ اَجْسَادِکُمْ وَ شَاہِدِکُمْ وَ غَآئِبِکُمْ \non your souls, on your bodies when you are visible, when you are invisible, on your perceivable aspects,\nوَ ظَاہِرِکُمْ وَ بَاطِنِکُمْ اٰمِیْنَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ.\non your innermost genius be it so, O Lord of the worlds.", 
    "title": "Ziyarah on the day of Arbaeen; The Twentieth of Safar"
}